  "action_title": "Plant riparian buffer strips",
  "key_messages": "Key Messages:\n\nOne replicated, controlled study in the USA\u00a0found that planting buffer strips along streams did not increase amphibian abundance, numbers of species, or the ratio of adults to tadpoles."
}

